            <title>[LU-12045] Ability to split test script execution into parts</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12045</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It is reported that it&apos;s possible to do ONLY=&quot;x-y&quot; to execute a range of tests.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Unfortunately that seems to no longer honor ALWAYS_EXCEPT and EXCEPT flags.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;so we need a way to reinstate that.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
